{"tid":1513604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"689母校都罷課！洗脫振英紀念中學之名","createTime":"2019-08-28T11:44:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T17:26:34.000Z","uid":169366,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a2b588cf20d660f24da0e682cd13b026776f7eff","tid":1513604,"uid":169366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:44:21.000Z","msg":"除左皇仁之外終於有官校跟機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【9月2日英皇反送中罷課籌備 召集在校生及校友聯署】<br />\n本關注組收到部分校友及在校學生查詢英皇有否罷課安排。為了協調成立在校學生反修例關注組，及協助同學與校方商討罷課安排，本組於此希望召集各位在校學生加入罷課籌委會，及各位校友教員冠名或出席支持學生參與罷課，以和平方式表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n罷課需要各位以不同型式支援，無論是在校生或是校友教員，都可以參與其中，或以冠名支持、或以協助與校方交涉、或以組織者身份一同參與。請各位在下表填寫相關資訊以加入相應telegram組群。我們將對各位提交的資料保密。<br />\n希望能在不同位置見到各學長學弟，We ourselves must write the story!<br />\n<br />\n表格及聯署連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/77R8fJS86NkuvPru8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F77R8fJS86NkuvPru8&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5HhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=a622d16f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/77R8fJS86NkuvPru8</a> <br />\n<br />\n#反送中 #902罷課 #五大訴求 #缺一不可 #護我英皇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KQezTJ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKQezTJ8.jpg&h=8e34603c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aafe60dd9b09fd1d757d78c384c2b054f1abb535","tid":1513604,"uid":169366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:45:20.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"6282cc9008f907a682a1db1cc9da88bfb8f5723a","tid":1513604,"uid":169366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:45:32.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"6ce6c2894832e8952d6228fcfe3e93cc2ed86d17","tid":1513604,"uid":169366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:45:45.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"03c755177ef3aca7e0d4c4db515075da2a48754f","tid":1513604,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:45:48